on Floor Five in Aincrad.

00:06:01.897 --> 00:06:04.101
I don’t think
I ever wanted anything more.

00:06:04.168 --> 00:06:06.606
Asuna: You mean
you hate Kirito so much,

00:06:06.673 --> 00:06:09.377
that you would cause
all this suffering?!

00:06:09.444 --> 00:06:10.748
Vassago: Say what?

00:06:10.815 --> 00:06:13.753
You of all people
should know better than that.

00:06:13.820 --> 00:06:15.456
I wouldn’t go
to all this trouble

00:06:15.524 --> 00:06:16.893
if I didn’t love the bastard.

00:06:18.296 --> 00:06:20.433
The world’s full of scumbags,

00:06:20.501 --> 00:06:23.472
in case you didn’t notice,
but that guy,

00:06:23.540 --> 00:06:25.510
he’s someone
you can totally believe in.

00:06:25.577 --> 00:06:28.449
No matter
how much I screwed with him

00:06:28.517 --> 00:06:31.288
or tried peelin’ back
that honor of his,

00:06:31.354 --> 00:06:32.858
he never took the bait.

00:06:32.925 --> 00:06:34.028
I respected that.

00:06:34.094 --> 00:06:35.363
Hell, I cheered him on!

00:06:35.430 --> 00:06:37.100
That’s why...

00:06:37.166 --> 00:06:38.837
seein’ him end up like that,

00:06:38.904 --> 00:06:42.578
I’m friggin’ pissed I wasn’t
the one that got to break him.

00:06:42.645 --> 00:06:45.483
But I’m gonna be the one
to snap him out of it.

00:06:45.551 --> 00:06:47.386
I’ll kill whoever I have to

00:06:47.453 --> 00:06:50.928
and however many I have to
to make that happen!

00:06:50.994 --> 00:06:52.932
( Asuna grunts )

00:06:52.999 --> 00:06:54.033
You’re sick.

00:06:54.100 --> 00:06:56.004
That’s why you’re doing this.

00:06:56.071 --> 00:06:57.373
You don’t respect him.

00:06:57.440 --> 00:06:59.812
You just get off
on making him suffer.

00:06:59.879 --> 00:07:00.947
You’re insane!

00:07:03.554 --> 00:07:05.289
- ( gasps )
- Vassago: Guess I finally

00:07:05.356 --> 00:07:07.494
got the hang
of how things work in here.

00:07:07.562 --> 00:07:09.531
Bet you didn’t know
all the spilled blood

00:07:09.598 --> 00:07:12.871
and lives lost in this world
get converted to energy.

00:07:12.938 --> 00:07:17.213
Back in Aincrad, any time
I used the ol’ Mate Chopper here

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:19.852
to kill a monster,
its stats would go down,

00:07:19.919 --> 00:07:22.758
but if I used it to kill
a person, they’d go up.

00:07:22.825 --> 00:07:25.463
Look at it now!
Here in the Underworld,

00:07:25.531 --> 00:07:27.801
it can suck
the energy from human lives

00:07:27.868 --> 00:07:31.809
right out of the air
and power up all on its own.

00:07:31.876 --> 00:07:34.615
Life energy’s
swirling all around us

00:07:34.682 --> 00:07:37.555
from the American players
you killed

00:07:37.621 --> 00:07:40.694
and from Japanese players
the Chinese and Koreans killed.

00:07:40.761 --> 00:07:43.767
And soon as they’re done
killing each other,

00:07:43.833 --> 00:07:46.806
this place is gonna be
overflowing with energy.

00:07:46.872 --> 00:07:49.845
My Chopper’s going
to absorb it all, and then...

00:07:49.912 --> 00:07:52.718
I’m gonna hunt down
every artificial Fluctlight

00:07:52.785 --> 00:07:54.822
and kill all of them, too.

00:07:54.889 --> 00:07:56.826
I’ll start
with the Dark Territory,

00:07:56.893 --> 00:08:00.099
then murder my way
across the Human Empire.

00:08:00.166 --> 00:08:01.570
What do you think, hot stuff?

00:08:01.636 --> 00:08:03.973
You think all that death’ll
wake him up?

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:07.113
If he’s the Black Swordsman
I remember, it will.

00:08:08.984 --> 00:08:11.088
( Asuna gasps )

00:08:11.155 --> 00:08:12.591
Vassago: Don’t you worry.

00:08:12.658 --> 00:08:14.929
You ain’t gonna die just yet.

00:08:14.996 --> 00:08:17.968
I’ll cut your arms and legs off
and keep you alive for a bit.

00:08:18.035 --> 00:08:21.609
I want you to stick around for
what I got planned for him...

00:08:23.012 --> 00:08:24.515
